choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.
Here's a sample healthy meal plan for today:

Breakfast: Oatmeal with fruit and nuts
Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, vegetables, and a vinaigrette dressing
Snack: Apple slices with almond butter
Dinner: Baked salmon with roasted vegetables
This meal plan provides a balance of protein, healthy fats, complex carbohydrates, and fiber to keep you feeling full and energized throughout the day. Enjoy!
